{"tid":706484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(要推就推呢個)香港都有整籃過機比錢用8達通，快過QR code","createTime":"2018-06-18T02:38:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T03:47:18.000Z","uid":81113,"like":55,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5bbb4cc863b2169518f06e35a18acc402bc27fbd","tid":706484,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T02:38:58.000Z","msg":"由於有條五毛開post踩港，所以特別開呢個post以正視聽<br />\n<br />\n其實香港都有整籃過機<br />\n而且唔係新野<br />\n我地香港仲可以8達通比錢一嘟ok<br />\n快撚過佢地開機-&gt;對焦-&gt;scan QR code<br />\n唔信你問下做收銀果d人<br />\n<br />\n屈臣氏推無人收銀「整籃」支付 毋須逐件掃碼<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/685587/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/685587/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/18/102508_cbaed4072abab377f87c06764cdf18a7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F18%2F102508_cbaed4072abab377f87c06764cdf18a7.png&h=4732f523&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以話香港落後簡直弱智<br />\n大陸落個大雨就水浸<br />\n水浸仲會電死人(無電無得用支那寶嘛，咪唔截電囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n邊個落後？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以以後見到咩香港落後既post，先諗諗係咪五毛搵錢post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下面五毛個post就唔好推喇，無謂比錢人賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去完深圳先知香港係幾咁落後<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/706163/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/706163/page/1</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c4a5efbbf3606320da84f06d5774552c01e86adf","tid":706484,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T02:45:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a5bfc96d45d08359b263ab93cd2ff3e514dc7847","tid":706484,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T02:47:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba9e